headline: Analysts Pick 2 ‘Tariff-Protected’ Stocks to Weather Macro Storms
summary: After months of uncertainty, President Trump unveiled his tariff policy last week – and to say the markets didn’t take it well would be a bit of an understatement. The announcement has triggered a wave of sharp market selloffs across the globe, shaking investor confidence and sparking fears of a looming recession.
